[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 11.4,
    "text": "What's up, guys? My name is Shane, and in today's video, you are going to learn some of the most common kitchen vocabulary and how to say those words like a native speaker."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.7,
    "endTime": 19.2,
    "text": "And make you sure watch until the end of the video because there will be a quiz to see how many words you can remember."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.4,
    "endTime": 20.933,
    "text": "Are you ready? Let's go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.266,
    "endTime": 25.099999999999998,
    "text": "This is a 'cutting board'. Cutting board."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.24,
    "endTime": 31.599999999999998,
    "text": "I know it's spelt with a 'T,' but when we pronounce it, we actually use a 'D' sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.7,
    "endTime": 34.3,
    "text": "Cudding board. Cudding board."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.4,
    "endTime": 39.333,
    "text": "And you can also call this a 'chopping board'. Chopping board."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.822,
    "endTime": 43.300000000000004,
    "text": "This is a 'colander'. Colander."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.4,
    "endTime": 46.933,
    "text": "Three sounds. Co-lan-der. Colander."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.48,
    "endTime": 52.099999999999994,
    "text": "This is a 'measuring jug'. Measuring jug."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.44,
    "endTime": 57.5,
    "text": "The 'S' in this word is pronounced the same as in the word 'television'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.55,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Television - 'sion'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 63.1,
    "text": "Measuring. Measuring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.2,
    "endTime": 64.733,
    "text": "Measuring jug."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.444,
    "endTime": 68.5,
    "text": "This is a 'pot'. Pot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.6,
    "endTime": 74.19999999999999,
    "text": "When we say this word, we stop the air with the final 'T' sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.3,
    "endTime": 77.1,
    "text": "We normally don't say 'poT'. No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.22,
    "endTime": 79.844,
    "text": "We say 'pot'. Pot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.622,
    "endTime": 86.088,
    "text": "This is a 'pan'. Pan. Pan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.844,
    "endTime": 90.86,
    "text": "This is an 'egg flip'. Egg flip."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.0,
    "endTime": 95.58,
    "text": "With that final 'P' sound, we stop the air from coming out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.66,
    "endTime": 98.02,
    "text": "We don't say 'fliP'. No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.1,
    "endTime": 101.93299999999999,
    "text": "We say 'flip'. Flip. Egg flip."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.355,
    "endTime": 107.77000000000001,
    "text": "This is a 'spatula'. Spatula. Spatula."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.87,
    "endTime": 112.5,
    "text": "The 'T' sound is actually pronounced as a 'CH' sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.68,
    "endTime": 116.022,
    "text": "Spa-chu-la. Spatula."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.8,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "These are 'tongs'. Tongs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.1,
    "endTime": 126.3,
    "text": "When we talk about tongs, we sometimes need to use the word 'pair'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.38,
    "endTime": 131.1,
    "text": "For example, 'I am holding a pair of tongs.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.2,
    "endTime": 134.28699999999998,
    "text": "We don't say, 'I am holding a tongs.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.933,
    "endTime": 138.2,
    "text": "This is a 'plate'. Plate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.26,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "With that final 'T' sound, we stop the air from coming out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.04,
    "endTime": 145.39,
    "text": "We don't say 'plaTe'. No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.47,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "We say 'plate'. Plate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.62,
    "endTime": 156.222,
    "text": "This is a 'bowl'. Bowl. B-owl. Bowl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.844,
    "endTime": 160.4,
    "text": "This is a 'glass'. Glass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.47,
    "endTime": 165.8,
    "text": "G-l-a-ss. Glass. Glass"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.555,
    "endTime": 169.6,
    "text": "This is a 'cup'. Cup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.75,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "When we say this word, we stop the air with that final 'P' sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.11,
    "endTime": 177.58,
    "text": "We don't say 'cuP'. No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.65,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "We say 'cup'. Cup."
