  {
    "startTime": 186.133,
    "endTime": 189.10000000000002,
    "text": "This is a 'knife'. Knife."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.2,
    "endTime": 194.29999999999998,
    "text": "The 'K' in this word is silent. That means we don't pronounce it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.35,
    "endTime": 197.37699999999998,
    "text": "So, when we pronounce this word, it's 'knife'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.133,
    "endTime": 202.20000000000002,
    "text": "These are 'spoons'. Spoons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.32,
    "endTime": 207.54999999999998,
    "text": "Normally, smaller spoons like this are called 'tea spoons'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.65,
    "endTime": 212.3,
    "text": "And bigger spoons like this one are called 'table spoons'."
