  {
    "startTime": 215.4,
    "endTime": 220.1,
    "text": "Did you know there is a word to describe these three things?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.25,
    "endTime": 223.6,
    "text": "It's called 'cutlery'. Cutlery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.73,
    "endTime": 234.86599999999999,
    "text": "So for example, if you go to a restaurant and you don't have a knife, a spoon and a fork, you can say, 'Excuse me, could I have some cutlery, please?' Cutlery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.555,
    "endTime": 240.15,
    "text": "This is a 'toaster'. Toaster. Toaster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.2,
    "endTime": 242.533,
    "text": "It's used to make toast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.4,
    "endTime": 248.3,
    "text": "This is a 'scales'. Scales. Scales."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.55,
    "endTime": 250.60000000000002,
    "text": "It's used to weigh things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.24,
    "endTime": 255.5,
    "text": "This is a 'blender'. Blender. Blender."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.77,
    "endTime": 260.022,
    "text": "It's used to make things like smoothies and milkshakes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.577,
    "endTime": 263.4,
    "text": "This is a 'jug'. Jug."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.66,
    "endTime": 266.87,
    "text": "You can also call it a 'kettle'. Kettle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.95,
    "endTime": 269.377,
    "text": "It's used to boil water."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.755,
    "endTime": 274.3,
    "text": "This is an 'oven'.  Oven.  Oven."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.53,
    "endTime": 279.0,
    "text": "With that 'V' sound, your throat should vibrate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.26,
    "endTime": 281.087,
    "text": "'Vvv.' Oven."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.666,
    "endTime": 286.022,
    "text": "These are 'oven mitts'. Oven mitts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.9,
    "endTime": 290.0,
    "text": "You put them on your hands to protect your hands when you're cooking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.24,
    "endTime": 291.088,
    "text": "Oven mitts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.4,
    "endTime": 296.4,
    "text": "This is a 'fridge'.  Fridge.  Fridge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.73,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "With that 'DG' sound, it sounds like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.0,
    "endTime": 305.5,
